# Real-run comparison report + artifact are REGENERATED on demand
# (`npm run compare:render`) from the committed history/ archives — the real-data
# source of truth. The rendered `.real` outputs are non-deterministic and not
# committed (unlike the byte-stable fixture `llm-model-comparison.md`/`.data.json`).
docs/research-reports/*.real.md
docs/research-reports/*.real.data.json
